lead_paragraph: Leicester City's triumphant coach Claudio Ranieri could one day win a World Cup for his native country, Italian Football Federation president Carlo Tavecchio said on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Ranieri Could One Day Win World Cup for Italy-Tavecchio
